        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review+1\n\n(1 comment)\n\nYou don't need to have separate test policy types and policies in policy API, you can simply add the examples modules from policy-models in your POM as a test dependency and use its examples for your test data. This means that if and as the examples change, you will be automatically validating that your code complies with the latest example policies.",
